Subject: BSD Deep Research Chow-Heegner Source Count 001

Description: Bounded Deep_Research_Priority_Gate pass on whether Chow-Heegner and related point constructions supply enough independent Mordell-Weil points for BSD source-count sufficiency.

& [DeepResearchUnit] is a Deep_Research_Priority_Gate application
  + [event_uuid] is a58a587b-0ea5-40bc-8d45-5fe1eea5d85c
  + [project] is seven math problems
