  + [meaning_gain] is source-document R-hand growth can mean a family of correspondences/cycles only after the target field, rank claim, and independence test are fixed
  + [proof_promotion] is blocked
    = reason: special explicit points and rank-one computations do not give enough independent generators for arbitrary BSD rank

